name: Search for pets by different status that don't exist

testSteps.description: Search for pets by different status that don't exist #1: {status=blablabla, response=[]}

children.description: Given I set base URL for search request to the petstore
And I set endpoint for  searching "/pet/findByStatus?status=blablabla"
And I set header for  request "accept" to value "application/json"
And And  I set operation for searching request to "GET"
When I search for pets with the corresponding status "blablabla"
Then the status code of search request should be a 200

dataTable.scenarioOutline:
Given I set base URL for search request to the petstore
And I set endpoint for  searching "/pet/findByStatus?status=<status>"
And I set header for  request "accept" to value "application/json"
And And  I set operation for searching request to "GET"
When I search for pets with the corresponding status "<status>"
Then the status code of search request should be a 200
